{"tid":2408570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓網熱帖】Lisa用中文拜年也被罵？韓網掀罵戰：明明還不是中國人","createTime":"2021-02-15T05:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T04:10:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbead010e66db86d4c0720bc65c7d7594039ee4","tid":2408570,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"在韓國各大線上討論區中，最近中韓網友就農曆新年的由來討論得十分熱烈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/14/550_1561061_1613292749.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F14%2F550_1561061_1613292749.webp&h=6b976e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中，BLACKPINK成員Lisa因用中文向粉絲們問候，更無辜被牽連，成為韓國網友討伐的對象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/14/550_1561063_1613292753.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F14%2F550_1561063_1613292753.webp&h=dbb5f908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13日下午，在韓網中，一名網友以「春節在中國進行新年問候的愛豆」為題上傳了一篇文章。<br />\n<br />\n上傳文章的人說到：「BLACKPINK Lisa在春節用中文在中國進行新年問候。最近(Lisa)在中國的選秀節目裡活動中，BLACKPINK真的是我們國家的愛豆嗎?」<br />\n<br />\n在這篇文章被發出後，馬上吸引了眾多網友閱讀及留言，得到了2000多的讚好及200多個「反對」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/02/14/550_1561060_1613292742.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F02%2F14%2F550_1561060_1613292742.webp&h=8ca5cbbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部分韓國網友留言表示：「對啊 為什麼她不用被說 明明連中國人都不是」、「明明不是中國人卻在中國問候ㅋㅋㅋ」、「原來大家不知道啊，Lisa在韓國出道獲得了人氣，為了宣傳中國選秀很忙碌^^(原本在韓國的)中國人愛豆通常都不會做韓國愛豆了，但Lisa卻是以現役身份堂堂正正地活動中呢^^」、「那個選秀節目不是搶了我們國家的Produce101嗎，真的反感了」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也有很多支持Lisa的網友，指出Lisa只是在幫忙宣傳節目的同時向觀眾說「Happy New Year」（甚至不是「Happy Chinese New Year」）。另外，有網友表示，Lisa有先向韓國粉絲以親筆信及畫畫進行親年問候，在中國的節目也是買了版權的，不懂為何某些人要為黑而黑。不知道大家又怎麼看呢?"},{"pid":"235ecc107d8d422f296b26100bb37885228cda40","tid":2408570,"uid":363330,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"中韓兩國啲人真係頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周身G點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3220ab709f7f94629a13f55effdde420a5c2d518","tid":2408570,"uid":4574,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"235ecc107d8d422f296b26100bb37885228cda40","tid":2408570,"uid":363330,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"中韓兩國啲人真係頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周身G點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"總之 支持韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687539e33b98443d4b88082eca967907522fb377","tid":2408570,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837118810b1644a42bcb1e9f8d5cb8c52e4d6153","tid":2408570,"uid":227992,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"佢唔係泰國人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2613ff6caea73ea05f6e039b7d8cd5730f54a0","tid":2408570,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"837118810b1644a42bcb1e9f8d5cb8c52e4d6153","tid":2408570,"uid":227992,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"佢唔係泰國人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"但佢係韓國做野"},{"pid":"0382bdeeb12ac8c2fd7fe326b538ba61050cd77c","tid":2408570,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"以為係汪明荃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84e3fdb7c38b7ba8a03c0eb065cae13a319a51f","tid":2408570,"uid":32051,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"理佢咁多<br />\n逢中必反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye